		"description":{
			"value":"<p><i>Created in ancient days by priests of Pelor, this weapon is the bane of undead everywhere.</i></p><p><b>Weapon</b><b>:</b> Flail, hammer or mace</p>\n<p><b>Enhancement Bonus:</b> Attack Rolls and Damage Rolls</p><p><b>Critical:</b> +6d6 radiant critical damage</p>\n<p><b>Properties:</b>\n<ul>\n<li>This weapon can be used as a holy symbol. It adds its enhancement bonus to attack rolls and damage rolls, and attacks can be augmented by this weapon's power when it is used as an implement. You do not gain your weapon proficiency to an attack roll when using a disrupting weapon as an implement.</li>\n<li>Critical deals +2d10 radiant damage against undead Level 13: +3d10 radiant damage Level 18: +4d10 radiant damage Level 23: +5d10 radiant damage Level 28: +6d10 radiant damage</li>\n</ul></p>\n<p><b>Power - Daily (Free Action)</b></p><p>Use this power when you hit an undead creature with this weapon. Deal +2d10 radiant damage.</p><p>Level 13: 3d10 radiant damage.</p><p>Level 18: 4d10 radiant damage.</p><p>Level 23: 5d10 radiant damage.</p><p>Level 28: 6d10 radiant damage.</p>",
